name: Version 4.3.1
body: Changed buienradar api uri, because old one was not working

name: Version 4.3.0
body:
added button to save current location
remembering current location instead of defaulting to De Bilt
remove old remove button images
change reload button to a fontawesome button
add radar map for rain
updated font-awesome

name: Version 4.1.1
body:
Fixed fetching raindata
Cosmetic change in display of temperature and wind

name: Version 4.1.0
body: Fixed not working due to api url change and re-added current weather info from OpenWeatherMap

name: Version 4.0.0
body: Updated Cordova framework to Cordova Android 5.1.0. This fixes geolocation issues in newer versions of Android

name: Version 3.1.0
body: Removed fetch currect weather from OpenWeatherMap due to a change in their API policy.

name: v3.0.0
body: Now using C3 charting library and not HighCharts anymore, because of the more open licence of C3. I also changed the name of the app in this release from Regenalarm and Rain Alarm to RegenTijd and RainTime. The app has no alarm and will not have an alarm in the future.

name: Version 2.2.1
body: Fixed menu and refresh icon for older devices

name: Version 1.1.0
body: This version shows a default location when the location is being determined in the background. Also adjusted the error messages.
